  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in the molcajete over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until translucent, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for an additional minute, stirring constantly.",
    "Stir in the ground cumin, smoked paprika, salt, and black pepper, and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the cooked kidney beans, diced tomatoes, and chopped parsley to the molcajete, and stir to combine.",
    "Reduce heat to low and simmer, covered, for 20 minutes, stirring occasionally.",
    "Taste and adjust the seasoning as needed.",
    "Serve the tagine hot, garnished with additional parsley if desired."
